OL,3,CSecond inquest into death of Ian
OL,4,CPaterson's patients hears from junior
OL,5,Ccolleague
OL,7,FA surgeon who worked alongside
OL,8,Fdisgraced breast surgeon Ian Paterson
OL,9,Fhas described him as "overpowering",
OL,10,Fas he gave evidence at the second
OL,11,Finquest into the deaths of his former
OL,12,Fpatients.
OL,14,FBala Subramanian worked alongside
OL,15,FPaterson as a junior surgeon at
OL,16,FHeartlands Hospital in Birmingham.
OL,18,FHe said that twice a week, there would
OL,19,Fbe meetings to discuss the treatment
OL,20,Fof individuals' patients.
