OL,7,FThis would involve a radiologist,
OL,8,Fconsultant surgeon, oncologist and
OL,9,Fnurses.
OL,11,FAt the time, Mr Subramanian was a
OL,12,Fjunior consultant, and he described
OL,13,FPaterson as "argumentative, abrupt and
OL,14,Foverpowering".
OL,16,FHe said he was "abrupt and someone who
OL,17,Fwouldn't take no for an answer", but
OL,18,Fhe added that generally during
OL,19,Fmeetings, everyone had their say.
