OL,7,FMr Subramanian was speaking on the
OL,8,Ffirst day of an inquest into the death
OL,9,Fof Elaine Turbill - the second inquest
OL,10,Finto the death of one of Paterson's
OL,11,Fvictims.
OL,13,FElaine Turbill who was 63 and from
OL,14,FSolihull, was diagnosed with breast
OL,15,Fcancer and had a mastectomy carried
OL,16,Fout by Paterson the following month.
