OL,7,FThe inquest at Birmingham and Solihull
OL,8,FCoroner's Court heard that Elaine, who
OL,9,Fworked as a legal secretary, had been
OL,10,Fmarried for 40 years and had two
OL,11,Fchildren.
OL,13,FIn a statement, her daughter Gemma
OL,14,Fsaid her mother was a "kind, loving
OL,15,Fand friendly person whose smile lit up
OL,16,Fa room. She enjoyed going to church,
OL,17,Fcooking and gardening and loved family
OL,18,Ftrips to Mablethorpe to "smell the sea
OL,19,Fair".
