OL,4,CPaterson's patients hears from junior
OL,5,Ccolleague
OL,7,FElaine Turbill died in 2017. Her
OL,8,Fdaughter said seven years on, the pain
OL,9,Fnever goes away.
OL,11,FShe said she feels her mother's death
OL,12,Fcould have been prevented which would
OL,13,Fhave given her the opportunity to see
OL,14,Fher second grandchild.
OL,16,FPaterson, who was based in Birmingham,
OL,17,Fis currently serving a 20-year
OL,18,Fsentence for his crimes, after
OL,19,Fcarrying out needless operations over
OL,20,Fa 14-year period.
