OL,5,Ccolleague
OL,7,FWhile working as a breast surgeon
OL,8,Fconsultant, he was diagnosing cancer
OL,9,Fwhen there wasn't any and cutting
OL,10,Fpatients open for no reason.
OL,12,FHe was found guilty in 2017 of 17
OL,13,Fcounts of wounding with intent and
OL,14,Fthree counts of unlawful wounding.
OL,16,FA total of 62 inquests have so far
OL,17,Fbeen opened on patients of Paterson,
OL,18,Fwho was employed by the Heart of
OL,19,FEngland NHS Foundation Trust, and
OL,20,Fpractised in the independent sector at
OL,21,FSpire Parkway and Spire Little Aston.
