OL,4,CPaterson's patients hears from junior
OL,5,Ccolleague
OL,7,FThe first inquest into the deaths of
OL,8,FPaterson's patients looked into the
OL,9,Fdeath of mother Chloe Nikitas, and
OL,10,Fheard that she was given a "cleavage-
OL,11,Fsparing" mastectomy by him, and then
OL,12,Fhad her breast cancer return.
OL,14,FChloe Nikitas, an environmental
OL,15,Fconsultant from Tamworth, was
OL,16,Fdiagnosed with breast cancer in 2002
OL,17,Fand was treated by the West Midlands
OL,18,F"butcher" surgeon.
OL,20,FThe inquest into her death continues.
